以為醫護罷工就係怕死，怕太多病人/特登同政府搞對抗<br />\n佢哋根本唔明醫護做咩罷工，醫護罷工係要封關阻截源頭，如果太多病人落嚟，多多醫護返工都唔夠，到時大量病人得唔同適當治療，都係攬住一齊死架咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:46:32.000Z","msg":"真係要講到佢哋明為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文宣重來都係咁用"},{"pid":"d624ab5cd5bc9ac688b9c6833f26b63bc5bfdd5a","tid":1861205,"uid":193371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb8e28cee8519ba7d65a7b0e623423316cb7642c","tid":1861205,"uid":42748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cab487b4f166148a1abd62e56b6e84e7d417812c","tid":1861205,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"好多人根本連醫護為乜罷工都唔知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"唔甘心場罷工因為文宣support唔夠而贏唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11170abd6efb54c1c49f5fb38a2dc9143fed7d6","tid":1861205,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"放一百個心。政府和藍絲講的野，連6歲小朋友都拆的掂。"},{"pid":"6ed282e32bca158870f93c818a1c89a0cc0e6694","tid":1861205,"uid":42748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"131c7fe3dd18cf744d0932958a6693fd54453a6c","tid":1861205,"uid":42748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9603ee38d0ddcb5f2c82b4e4872560420ee98a40","tid":1861205,"uid":42748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e11170abd6efb54c1c49f5fb38a2dc9143fed7d6","tid":1861205,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"放一百個心。政府和藍絲講的野，連6歲小朋友都拆的掂。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"可惜幾咁on9嘅嘢都有大把藍絲廢老信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613a8d57909f322b305a0dcb124cd56031c502b3","tid":1861205,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf51e9b276f6dee4b3f020216e84b3f9d93c45ca","tid":1861205,"uid":61282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"文宣告急呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁多藍絲港豬以為醫護罷工就係怕死，怕太多病人/特登同政府搞對抗<br />\n佢哋根本唔明醫護做咩罷工，醫護罷工係要封關阻截源頭，如果太多病人落嚟，多多醫護返工都唔夠，到時大量病人得唔同適當治療，都係攬住一齊死架咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:52:27.000Z","msg":"認埋佢都仲得啦！淨系你識怕死？醫護唔怕死？醫護都怕死，政府沒有提供一個安全的社會環境比醫護，安慰醫護。咁你仲要醫護唔怕死？除非醫護全部都系傻的。"},{"pid":"6bea102ceeca6e20e3141ec3cb2f1a13df3d906a","tid":1861205,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0702725435977b05323e652ac21fa3f951e37d4f","tid":1861205,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2DsitZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2DsitZ.png&h=ca890e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CJx448Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCJx448Z.png&h=18cbf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZCsXFHk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZCsXFHk.png&h=379e55d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"另一種講法。<br />\n<br />\n醫護罷工系為了保存醫療系統的負壓力。香港每日有帶菌者進入香港，待社區爆發後，香港醫護必定全部染病。所以要醫護先藏起來，避免香港陷入醫療系統崩壞的局面而不可收拾。<br />\n<br />\n咁至於香港是否必定會社區爆發呢？按林鄭呢個豬頭炳宜家的政策來睇，我就覺得一定會。"}]}